Hi there!
 
First of all, I would like to THANK YOU and CONGRATULATIONS for the great job in this useful class! I use it a lot!
 
Now, I´m trying to saving a XLS file on version 2007, but can´t open with my Excel 2003 SP2 Version. Is it possible? When I try to open the XLS file, I get the message "Unrecognize XLS Format".
 
 
$objWriter = new PHPExcel_Writer_Excel2007($objPHPExcel);
$objWriter->setOffice2003Compatibility(true);
$objWriter->save(str_replace('.php', '.xls', __FILE__));
 
 
Writting on Version Excel5 it works perfectly!
Thanks , Aldo
